<li id="cite_note-23"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.cbeta.org/result/normal/T50/2060_016.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.cbeta.org/result/normal/T50/2060_016.htm" rel="nofollow"><i>Taishō Shinshū Daizōkyō</i>, Vol. 50, No. 2060</a>, p. 551c 06(02)</li>
